" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;فنعم \n   اليوم يوم الأربعاء</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;و \n   في يوم الخميس قضاء حاجة</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   ففيه الله يأذن بالدعاء</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   و في الجمعات تزويج و عرس</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   و لذات الرجال مع النساء</td>\n  </tr>\n    <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   و هذا العلم لا يعلمه إلا</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   نبي أو وصي الأنبياء</td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>\n  \n</div>\n","ديوان الإمام علي(ع)"]